<br />\n<br />\n合 理 地 恐 懼 身 體 會 遭 受 暴 力 或 疾 病 危 害； <br />\n<br />\n受 僱 主 苛 待； 或 <br />\n<br />\n已 受 僱 不 少 於 五 年， 並 經 註 冊 醫 生 證 明 永 久 不 適 合 擔 任 目 前 的 工 作。"},{"pid":"75bd393dece87d4b06ea6103160cc168e85cc463","tid":43478,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿爺唔批，佢可以做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勞工處求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bc162758c2b16f458a6d6dd158b78657a8a6a2","tid":43478,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"屌，每份合約都應該有通知期，過左你唔批都應該當離職，理鳩得你"},{"pid":"9a021a5578b455ac776943de2df29cb06d3c17c1","tid":43478,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地仲笑得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />金翅仆街鳥，下屆沐病</blockquote><br />\n689上任第一日50萬人上街<br />\n淋病會唔會超越689?</blockquote><br />\n對上一次唔係反廿三條咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8fe2734d0b324650ec6518780f777420bc9af3","tid":43478,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地仲笑得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />金翅仆街鳥，下屆沐病</blockquote><br />\n689上任第一日50萬人上街<br />\n淋病會唔會超越689?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淋病宜家民望仲好高<br />\n<br />\n當年係唐唐係論壇拆穿689真面目先咁多人上街"},{"pid":"0103e74f39428f89d9a11a97dcac1a7aee14ae2f","tid":43478,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:01:16.000Z","msg":"算啦, 下屆林鄭呢D濕9做架啦"},{"pid":"f736168ca7c7b5687e0343bf131f89b4d4f8f793","tid":43478,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"公務員行公務員條例架"},{"pid":"8f4277bcedf6565e069cd03569328934a207cac3","tid":43478,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":